    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Fog Lights (Optional)</title>
        <para>The fog lights are located at the center opening (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f47006140">Figure 140, Item 1</hotlnk>) of the front bumper assembly.
        </para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Tilt the hood forward.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Locate the fog light assembly harness and connection.</para>
            <figure id="f47006140" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figg47/G47006140.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="272px"
                         scalefitheight="272px"/>
                <caption>Figure 140. Chassis Fog Lights</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1>1. FOG LIGHT ASSEMBLY</callout1>
                    <callout1>2. RADIATOR CORE</callout1>
                    <callout1>3. BUMPER CROSS BAR ASSEMBLY</callout1>
                    <callout1>4. BUMPER ASSEMBLY</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <figure id="f47006141" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figg47/G47006141.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="272px"
                         scalefitheight="272px"/>
                <caption>Figure 141. Fog Light Removal</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1>1. BUMPER ASSEMBLY</callout1>
                    <callout1>2. FOG LIGHT ASSEMBLIES</callout1>
                    <callout1>3. FRONT CROSS MEMBER ASSEMBLY</callout1>
                    <callout1>4. FOG LIGHT MOUNTING BOLT AND MOUNTING HOLE</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Disconnect the harness from hood harness.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Loosen and remove fog light mounting nut and flat washer (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f47006141">Figure 141, Item 4</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove fog light assembly.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Locate and remove lens ring screws to gain access to fog light bulb.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the bulb and replace if required.</para>
            <para>Follow same procedure for removal of opposite side fog light.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcsubproc>
